类 RepresentativeByteArrayIterator<T extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.giraph.utils.ByteArrayIterator<T>
      • org.apache.giraph.utils.RepresentativeByteArrayIterator<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - Type that extends Writable that will be iterated
    所有已实现的接口:
    Iterator<T>

    public abstract class RepresentativeByteArrayIterator<T extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>
extends ByteArrayIterator<T>
    The objects provided by this iterator have lifetimes only until next() is called. In that sense, the object provided is only a representative object.
